::Prowl::

Prowl looks up at Iron Raptor, pulling himself to his feet.

"I'm allright. Are you feeling ok, love?" He could feel that she was
tired, and he was too, but there was something more to her. He walks
over to her and stretches out an arm so she could hold on if she
wanted. He wanted to kiss her, but there was currently a battle raging
around them.

been the

the
